Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥和一个陌生的女人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的那个人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙真的和女人在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急事就是指这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}而且对方还比他年长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在接受补习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师原来喜欢这种类型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  她不是刚才我看到的那个女人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有小孩的啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假的  这一定是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不亲眼看到我才不会相信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去确认一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被他发现了会很不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点是无需担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了应对这种情况我早就进行了量产
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  这算乔装吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是专业人士的手段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊  千枝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐  请不要这么快就开始爆笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年长这么多！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看上去好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足立这家伙又把事情给搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来还要再花点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  明明约好和你一起逛庙会的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Loveling？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探要是放弃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件可就无法破获了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你可不能放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要坚持到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能…放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,品行调查就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若对爱感到疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用魔法之力来迅速解决
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,品行调查就请交给敝公司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女侦探Loveling
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪亮登场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  为什么卖光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  有个操着一口奇怪口音的外国美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用令人难以置信的气势全吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把店里的刨冰全都吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给Loveling吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想叫外卖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能送冰块过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的会送来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  哥哥曾说过她是个很厉害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Loveling是遇到困难的人们的伙伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给我一份刨冰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  卖光了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把那个借我用一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请善用我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Loveling是遇到困难的人们的伙伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  很合适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里应该说「可爱」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要我来帮你拍拍背吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为我会死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔是卖烟火的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说烟火也是一门艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢在庙会中像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着等待放烟火的客人们的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只要我把烟火放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的所有人都会露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让别人露出笑容是一件很了不起的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让别人露出笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  差不多到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:18:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要放个大烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子  你这身打扮是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  快看烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  放烟火了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让别人露出笑容是一件很了不起的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥很了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家都笑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥很了不起哦  了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  玩的开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来后天会有好东西寄过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜  西瓜在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}西瓜  究竟在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  完二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么贪图别人送的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.15,0:21:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅正在过去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是期待不已啊  打西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  要打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子也想打
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞溅的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绽放的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一日元的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天的青涩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是青春
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是青春
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多双鞋啊  来了多少人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  我想打西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没考虑过要打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子  下次有机会再来打西瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.35,0:22:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打的话就在海边打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.96,0:22:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好主意  去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过从时间上来说可能要等到明年了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家明年也能陪菜菜子玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.46,0:22:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊  菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.50,0:23:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  西瓜真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.58,0:23:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.27,0:23:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜真好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假里你都在干些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想被打成马蜂窝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这说来话长…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,187)\1c000000\bord0\shad0\b1}数天前
Comment: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.58,0:24:18.08,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}下条线索
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要让我帮他实现这个愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.47,0:24:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让大家为难
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.17,0:24:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我们要不要两人一起去哪玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.39,0:24:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小勇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.25,0:24:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后能遇到你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.85,0:24:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的  「Neo Feather Man」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.88,0:24:31.43,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}下集  一个暴风雨般的暑假  2/2


